# Engineering Items

## Gnome Technology

Examples of Gnome Technology:

***[Gnomecorder](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Gnomecorder).*** _Rare or uncommon_ Vast improvements over the bulky buzzboxes. Small, about the size of a brick. You can set the gnomecorder to specific channels, allowing communication to anyone else on that channel within range--friend or foe. A gnomecorder's range is about 50 miles in optimal conditions, but like the buzzbox can have the signal degraded by obstruction and weather.

***[Gyroparasol](https://wow.gamepedia.com/Gyroparasol).***

